♪ The door that finally opens ♪

00:16.000 --> 00:18.000
♪ With light flooding in ♪

00:18.000 --> 00:22.000
♪ Spilling out on the floor ♪

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
♪♪

00:24.000 --> 00:28.000
♪ The core that never was ♪

00:28.000 --> 00:31.000
♪ Now it will be ♪

00:31.000 --> 00:36.000
♪ The bones of

00:31.000 --> 00:36.000
what was there before ♪

00:36.000 --> 00:39.000
♪ Every step, every beat ♪

00:39.000 --> 00:43.000
♪ Every thought, every breath,

00:39.000 --> 00:43.000
everything ♪

00:43.000 --> 00:48.000
♪ Is longing ♪

00:48.000 --> 00:50.000
♪♪

00:50.000 --> 00:54.000
♪ Pulling you from the sky ♪

00:54.000 --> 00:57.000
♪ Just like love will do ♪

00:57.000 --> 01:01.000
♪ Pulling you from the ground ♪

01:01.000 --> 01:04.000
♪ Just like love will do ♪

01:04.000 --> 01:13.000
♪♪

01:33.000 --> 01:36.000
[ Rumbling in distance ]

01:36.000 --> 01:39.000
♪♪

01:39.000 --> 01:41.000
[ Can clatters ]

01:41.000 --> 01:44.000
♪♪

01:44.000 --> 01:46.000
Mother?

01:46.000 --> 01:49.000
♪♪

01:49.000 --> 01:52.000
Mother, are you there?

01:52.000 --> 02:00.000
♪♪

02:00.000 --> 02:02.000
Mother, where are you?

02:02.000 --> 02:05.000
♪♪

02:05.000 --> 02:07.000
Mother?

02:07.000 --> 02:15.000
♪♪

02:15.000 --> 02:24.000
♪♪

02:24.000 --> 02:25.000
Otho: Release me

02:24.000 --> 02:25.000
from this prison

02:25.000 --> 02:27.000
so that I may

02:25.000 --> 02:27.000
see your light again.

02:27.000 --> 02:29.000
[ Gasps ]

02:29.000 --> 02:34.000
Light, sound,

02:29.000 --> 02:34.000
feel your feeling.

02:34.000 --> 02:36.000
Set me free.

02:37.000 --> 02:41.000
Do not despise me

02:37.000 --> 02:41.000
for my weakness.

02:41.000 --> 02:45.000
Grant me the power

02:41.000 --> 02:45.000
of your light

02:45.000 --> 02:51.000
so that I may bear your whip

02:45.000 --> 02:51.000
and purify this wicked planet.

02:51.000 --> 02:55.000
Simply purge these shadows

02:51.000 --> 02:55.000
from my sight,

02:55.000 --> 03:01.000
and I promise you

02:55.000 --> 03:01.000
I will deliver your judgment.

03:01.000 --> 03:04.000
I am your one true Sol.

03:04.000 --> 03:08.000
I am ready

03:04.000 --> 03:08.000
to receive your power.

03:08.000 --> 03:13.000
Just say the word,

03:08.000 --> 03:13.000
and I will be --

03:13.000 --> 03:15.000
Tempest: Hey.

03:15.000 --> 03:18.000
[ Electronic scanning ]

03:18.000 --> 03:24.000
♪♪

03:24.000 --> 03:29.000
♪♪

03:30.000 --> 03:32.000
Do you know who I am?

03:32.000 --> 03:34.000
Have we met?

03:35.000 --> 03:36.000
No.

03:36.000 --> 03:38.000
We never met.

03:38.000 --> 03:42.000
But you know me.

03:42.000 --> 03:44.000
You raise a weapon against me,

03:42.000 --> 03:44.000
child?

03:44.000 --> 03:47.000
I was sleeping,

03:44.000 --> 03:47.000
you sick bastard!

03:47.000 --> 03:48.000
I remember now.

03:48.000 --> 03:51.000
And I also remember

03:48.000 --> 03:51.000
how small you are.

03:52.000 --> 03:53.000
Careful, dear.

03:53.000 --> 03:54.000
You can't hurt me again.

03:54.000 --> 03:56.000
That helmet prevents it.

03:56.000 --> 03:58.000
So tell me --

03:56.000 --> 03:58.000
You tell me

03:58.000 --> 04:02.000
how does it feel knowing that

03:58.000 --> 04:02.000
I can do whatever I want to you,

04:02.000 --> 04:03.000
and you can't stop me?

04:03.000 --> 04:05.000
Mother: No, Tempest!

04:05.000 --> 04:07.000
Mother?

04:07.000 --> 04:09.000
[ Wheezing ]

04:09.000 --> 04:11.000
Mother.

04:11.000 --> 04:12.000
There's no need

04:11.000 --> 04:12.000
to hurt me.

04:12.000 --> 04:14.000
Where's your guard?

04:14.000 --> 04:15.000
It's in the backpack.

04:16.000 --> 04:17.000
What are you doing?

04:17.000 --> 04:22.000
♪♪

04:22.000 --> 04:24.000
What functions do you

04:22.000 --> 04:24.000
still have available?

04:24.000 --> 04:26.000
Proximity trigger active.

04:26.000 --> 04:29.000
Behavioral guard

04:26.000 --> 04:29.000
in the helmet is...

04:29.000 --> 04:31.000
checking status...

04:29.000 --> 04:31.000
active.

04:31.000 --> 04:33.000
What's the maximum distance

04:31.000 --> 04:33.000
he's allowed from you

04:33.000 --> 04:35.000
before the helmet

04:33.000 --> 04:35.000
kills him?

04:35.000 --> 04:36.000
10 feet.

04:36.000 --> 04:38.000
I want to kill him.

04:38.000 --> 04:40.000
I understand that,

04:38.000 --> 04:40.000
Tempest.

04:40.000 --> 04:41.000
[ Metal clanks ]

04:41.000 --> 04:42.000
Do you?

04:43.000 --> 04:45.000
Every time

04:43.000 --> 04:45.000
I feel this baby move,

04:45.000 --> 04:48.000
I'm forced to think of

04:45.000 --> 04:48.000
this piece of shit raping me.

04:48.000 --> 04:50.000
Does this port allow

04:48.000 --> 04:50.000
for blood draw?

04:50.000 --> 04:52.000
Yes, of course.

04:50.000 --> 04:52.000
Mother,

04:50.000 --> 04:52.000
are you listening to me?

04:52.000 --> 04:53.000
What's the color

04:52.000 --> 04:53.000
for outflow?

04:54.000 --> 04:56.000
Red.

04:54.000 --> 04:56.000
Mother!

04:56.000 --> 04:58.000
Mother,

04:56.000 --> 04:58.000
I'm talking to you!

04:58.000 --> 05:00.000
[ Beeping ]

05:00.000 --> 05:04.000
♪♪

05:04.000 --> 05:06.000
What are you doing?

05:06.000 --> 05:08.000
[ Grunts ]

05:08.000 --> 05:11.000
♪♪

05:11.000 --> 05:13.000
I'm feeding my fetus.

05:13.000 --> 05:15.000
♪♪

05:15.000 --> 05:17.000
Your fetus?

05:17.000 --> 05:24.000
♪♪

05:24.000 --> 05:30.000
♪♪

05:30.000 --> 05:32.000
Tell me

05:30.000 --> 05:32.000
where they went.

05:32.000 --> 05:38.000
♪♪

05:38.000 --> 05:40.000
All alone now.

05:40.000 --> 05:43.000
♪♪

05:44.000 --> 05:46.000
Tell me where they went.

05:46.000 --> 05:50.000
♪♪

05:50.000 --> 05:52.000
I did all you wanted me to.

05:53.000 --> 05:56.000
Now come on.

05:56.000 --> 05:59.000
Help me get my son back.

05:59.000 --> 06:03.000
♪♪

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
Father: Poor idiots

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
are gonna die out there.

06:05.000 --> 06:07.000
Can't believe they took off

06:05.000 --> 06:07.000
without telling me,

06:07.000 --> 06:11.000
after everything

06:07.000 --> 06:11.000
I've done for them.

06:11.000 --> 06:14.000
Can't listen to that thing

06:11.000 --> 06:14.000
anymore.

06:14.000 --> 06:17.000
Start loading the lander

06:14.000 --> 06:17.000
with food and supplies.

06:17.000 --> 06:19.000
Reinstall

06:17.000 --> 06:19.000
the lift drive module.

06:42.000 --> 06:44.000
[ Computer pinging ]

06:44.000 --> 06:48.000
My holo-screen appears

06:44.000 --> 06:48.000
to have self-activated.

06:48.000 --> 06:51.000
Huh.

06:51.000 --> 06:54.000
Probably some malfunction

06:51.000 --> 06:54.000
caused by the amputation.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.000
♪♪

06:56.000 --> 06:58.000
Hold on.

06:58.000 --> 07:04.000
♪♪

07:04.000 --> 07:07.000
Revert

07:04.000 --> 07:07.000
to old program.

07:07.000 --> 07:10.000
Password.

07:07.000 --> 07:10.000
Password...

07:10.000 --> 07:12.000
Shit.

07:12.000 --> 07:17.000
♪♪

07:18.000 --> 07:19.000
It's Morse code.

07:19.000 --> 07:21.000
♪♪

07:21.000 --> 07:23.000
Sol is the light.

07:23.000 --> 07:27.000
♪♪

07:27.000 --> 07:29.000
Sol is...

07:29.000 --> 07:31.000
the light.

07:31.000 --> 07:37.000
♪♪

07:37.000 --> 07:41.000
Hey, Father.

07:41.000 --> 07:42.000
Say something.

07:42.000 --> 07:45.000
♪♪

07:45.000 --> 07:47.000
Father?

07:47.000 --> 07:52.000
♪♪

07:52.000 --> 07:54.000
An android, a black hole,

07:54.000 --> 07:56.000
and a glass of milk

07:54.000 --> 07:56.000
walk into a bar.

07:56.000 --> 07:57.000
Father!

07:57.000 --> 08:00.000
Marcus: Alright.

07:57.000 --> 08:00.000
Let's go.

08:00.000 --> 08:02.000
I'll finish this joke

08:00.000 --> 08:02.000
at a later date.

08:02.000 --> 08:05.000
You need to convince them to

08:02.000 --> 08:05.000
take you along on the search.

08:05.000 --> 08:07.000
♪♪

08:08.000 --> 08:09.000
Thank you.

08:09.000 --> 08:16.000
♪♪

08:16.000 --> 08:19.000
Let's go, Pop.

08:19.000 --> 08:21.000
Wait,

08:19.000 --> 08:21.000
can I come with you?

08:21.000 --> 08:23.000
I know the kids well,

08:21.000 --> 08:23.000
like family.

08:23.000 --> 08:24.000
I could help wrangle them.

08:24.000 --> 08:27.000
They trust me.

08:24.000 --> 08:27.000
Hmm.

08:27.000 --> 08:29.000
You didn't do such a good job

08:27.000 --> 08:29.000
of wrangling them

08:29.000 --> 08:31.000
last night,

08:29.000 --> 08:31.000
though, did you?

08:31.000 --> 08:35.000
♪♪

08:35.000 --> 08:38.000
[ Sighs ]

08:35.000 --> 08:38.000
You coming or not?

08:38.000 --> 08:43.000
♪♪

08:44.000 --> 08:46.000
How will we track them without

08:44.000 --> 08:46.000
the locators, Your Eminence?

08:46.000 --> 08:50.000
We're going back

08:46.000 --> 08:50.000
to the temple.

08:50.000 --> 08:51.000
Sol will speak to me there.

08:51.000 --> 08:56.000
♪♪

08:56.000 --> 08:59.000
[ Ship powering up ]

08:59.000 --> 09:03.000
♪♪

09:03.000 --> 09:05.000
[ Wind howling ]

09:05.000 --> 09:09.000
♪♪

09:09.000 --> 09:11.000
[ Shivering ]

09:35.000 --> 09:37.000
[ Squeaking ]

09:37.000 --> 09:45.000
♪♪

09:45.000 --> 09:47.000
Paul: Sol brought him

09:45.000 --> 09:47.000
back to me.

09:47.000 --> 09:50.000
♪♪

09:50.000 --> 09:52.000
You said

09:50.000 --> 09:52.000
he fell down a pit.

09:52.000 --> 09:53.000
He did.

09:53.000 --> 09:57.000
But I prayed for Sol to give him

09:53.000 --> 09:57.000
back to me, and it worked.

09:57.000 --> 09:59.000
So now

09:57.000 --> 09:59.000
you don't have to wonder

09:59.000 --> 10:03.000
whether or not

09:59.000 --> 10:03.000
Sol is real anymore.

10:03.000 --> 10:04.000
So now you have proof.

10:04.000 --> 10:07.000
♪♪

10:07.000 --> 10:09.000
My sister Tally fell down a pit

10:07.000 --> 10:09.000
when we were small.

10:10.000 --> 10:12.000
♪♪

10:12.000 --> 10:13.000
When I was locked up

10:12.000 --> 10:13.000
in the silo,

10:13.000 --> 10:16.000
she came back

10:13.000 --> 10:16.000
and talked to me.

10:16.000 --> 10:19.000
Only she was different.

10:19.000 --> 10:21.000
What's the word?

10:21.000 --> 10:23.000
Evil?

10:23.000 --> 10:27.000
♪♪

10:28.000 --> 10:29.000
Sue: Hey, come on.

10:28.000 --> 10:29.000
We got to get moving.

10:29.000 --> 10:31.000
We're too out in the open here.

10:31.000 --> 10:33.000
Pack everything you can.

10:33.000 --> 10:35.000
Girls, please, wake up.

10:33.000 --> 10:35.000
Get up.

10:35.000 --> 10:42.000
♪♪

10:42.000 --> 10:50.000
♪♪

10:50.000 --> 10:54.000
Sol, tell me where they are,

10:50.000 --> 10:54.000
please.

10:54.000 --> 10:56.000
♪♪

10:57.000 --> 10:58.000
I will do anything.

10:58.000 --> 11:03.000
♪♪

11:03.000 --> 11:05.000
Does my son not trust me?

11:05.000 --> 11:09.000
♪♪

11:10.000 --> 11:13.000
Does he not love me?

11:13.000 --> 11:16.000
Please tell me.

11:16.000 --> 11:18.000
Vita: Why are we here?

11:18.000 --> 11:21.000
Sue: 'Cause you never know

11:18.000 --> 11:21.000
what we might find.

11:21.000 --> 11:25.000
You know, food,

11:21.000 --> 11:25.000
supplies, water.

11:25.000 --> 11:27.000
The stuff for survival.

11:27.000 --> 11:28.000
Campion: I can't believe

11:27.000 --> 11:28.000
something so big

11:28.000 --> 11:30.000
could actually fly.

11:30.000 --> 11:32.000
It must have been

11:30.000 --> 11:32.000
magnificent.

11:42.000 --> 11:45.000
Holly: This is one of the relics

11:42.000 --> 11:45.000
we brought from Earth.

11:46.000 --> 11:48.000
A tooth?

11:48.000 --> 11:51.000
It was taken from the body

11:48.000 --> 11:51.000
of Romulus.

11:51.000 --> 11:55.000
He and his brother were raised

11:51.000 --> 11:55.000
by a she-wolf who lost her cubs.

11:59.000 --> 12:01.000
We have to

11:59.000 --> 12:01.000
keep it safe.

12:01.000 --> 12:04.000
I found it

12:01.000 --> 12:04.000
for a reason.

12:04.000 --> 12:06.000
A reason.

12:06.000 --> 12:10.000
Sol led us here so that

12:06.000 --> 12:10.000
we could find this holy relic,

12:10.000 --> 12:12.000
so that we can

12:10.000 --> 12:12.000
save our culture.

12:12.000 --> 12:14.000
Keep your teeth.

12:12.000 --> 12:14.000
I don't care.

12:14.000 --> 12:16.000
Now, if you can please

12:14.000 --> 12:16.000
look for things

12:16.000 --> 12:19.000
we can actually use,

12:16.000 --> 12:19.000
that would be great.

12:19.000 --> 12:21.000
Campion: Blood!

12:21.000 --> 12:26.000
♪♪

12:27.000 --> 12:32.000
♪♪

12:32.000 --> 12:34.000
It's fresh.

12:34.000 --> 12:36.000
Tempest.

12:36.000 --> 12:38.000
It could be

12:36.000 --> 12:38.000
from anyone.

12:38.000 --> 12:43.000
♪♪

12:43.000 --> 12:44.000
Tempest: Hold up.

12:44.000 --> 12:46.000
You got pregnant

12:44.000 --> 12:46.000
in a sim pod?

12:46.000 --> 12:48.000
Mother: Yes.

12:48.000 --> 12:50.000
I didn't even know androids

12:48.000 --> 12:50.000
could get pregnant.

12:50.000 --> 12:52.000
Nor did I.

12:52.000 --> 12:54.000
How did it happen?

12:54.000 --> 12:56.000
It's beyond

12:54.000 --> 12:56.000
my understanding.

12:56.000 --> 12:59.000
My creator

12:56.000 --> 12:59.000
made it possible.

12:59.000 --> 13:01.000
You sound religious

12:59.000 --> 13:01.000
suddenly.

13:01.000 --> 13:04.000
Nonsense.

13:04.000 --> 13:06.000
So, now that

13:04.000 --> 13:06.000
you're all pregnant,

13:06.000 --> 13:08.000
your programming tells you

13:06.000 --> 13:08.000
to turn away

13:08.000 --> 13:10.000
the girl that you said

13:08.000 --> 13:10.000
you'd never leave?

13:12.000 --> 13:16.000
You're referring

13:12.000 --> 13:16.000
to the other day.

13:16.000 --> 13:18.000
I had to send you away,

13:16.000 --> 13:18.000
Tempest.

13:18.000 --> 13:19.000
Otherwise I could have

13:18.000 --> 13:19.000
put you in danger.

13:19.000 --> 13:22.000
You're not

13:19.000 --> 13:22.000
a danger to me.

13:22.000 --> 13:26.000
I feel the urge

13:22.000 --> 13:26.000
to protect you.

13:26.000 --> 13:29.000
I also feel the need

13:26.000 --> 13:29.000
to feed my fetus.

13:29.000 --> 13:35.000
♪♪

13:35.000 --> 13:37.000
You were afraid

13:35.000 --> 13:37.000
you would --

13:37.000 --> 13:39.000
My programming has

13:37.000 --> 13:39.000
become unpredictable.

13:39.000 --> 13:40.000
It was just

13:39.000 --> 13:40.000
a precaution.

13:40.000 --> 13:44.000
♪♪

13:44.000 --> 13:46.000
Okay, but where

13:44.000 --> 13:46.000
are we even going?

13:47.000 --> 13:53.000
To a place where the delivery

13:47.000 --> 13:53.000
is most likely to be successful.

13:53.000 --> 13:57.000
Otho: Child, you must see this

13:53.000 --> 13:57.000
necromancer's malfunctioning.

13:57.000 --> 13:59.000
She has no need

13:57.000 --> 13:59.000
for human blood,

13:59.000 --> 14:01.000
and she's certainly

13:59.000 --> 14:01.000
not pregnant.

14:01.000 --> 14:03.000
She is insane.

14:03.000 --> 14:05.000
And she'll turn on you.

14:05.000 --> 14:07.000
She is the threat,

14:05.000 --> 14:07.000
not me.

14:07.000 --> 14:08.000
One more word out of you,

14:08.000 --> 14:10.000
and I will skewer

14:08.000 --> 14:10.000
your metal head.

14:11.000 --> 14:20.000
♪♪

14:20.000 --> 14:29.000
♪♪

14:29.000 --> 14:38.000
♪♪

14:38.000 --> 14:39.000
What is it?

14:39.000 --> 14:41.000
Metal.

14:41.000 --> 14:49.000
♪♪

14:49.000 --> 14:56.000
♪♪

14:56.000 --> 15:04.000
♪♪

15:04.000 --> 15:11.000
♪♪

15:11.000 --> 15:14.000
These were placed here

15:11.000 --> 15:14.000
recently.

15:14.000 --> 15:16.000
By who?

15:16.000 --> 15:21.000
♪♪

15:21.000 --> 15:24.000
This one reminds me

15:21.000 --> 15:24.000
of you and Father.

15:24.000 --> 15:31.000
♪♪

15:31.000 --> 15:34.000
And that one's

15:31.000 --> 15:34.000
Sol Invictus.

15:35.000 --> 15:37.000
These remind me of the old

15:35.000 --> 15:37.000
Tarot cards back on Earth.

15:37.000 --> 15:40.000
Used by the devil cults

15:37.000 --> 15:40.000
before we purged their ranks.

15:40.000 --> 15:42.000
Quiet.

15:42.000 --> 15:43.000
Something's approaching.

15:44.000 --> 15:45.000
Hide.

15:45.000 --> 15:49.000
♪♪

15:49.000 --> 15:52.000
Otho,

15:49.000 --> 15:52.000
hide yourself!

15:52.000 --> 15:58.000
♪♪

15:58.000 --> 16:00.000
Sue: You think

15:58.000 --> 16:00.000
you can walk now?

16:01.000 --> 16:02.000
Vita: Yep.

16:02.000 --> 16:04.000
Alright.

16:04.000 --> 16:06.000
-Maybe in a little bit.

16:04.000 --> 16:06.000
-There's more blood.

16:06.000 --> 16:10.000
What?

16:10.000 --> 16:11.000
Campion!

16:11.000 --> 16:13.000
-Mother?

16:11.000 --> 16:13.000
-Campion!

16:13.000 --> 16:14.000
Campion: Mother!

16:14.000 --> 16:15.000
Vita: Tempest!

16:16.000 --> 16:17.000
I thought I'd never

16:16.000 --> 16:17.000
see you again!

16:17.000 --> 16:19.000
-I knew you were alive!

16:17.000 --> 16:19.000
[ Gunshot ]

16:19.000 --> 16:22.000
Step away from the android,

16:19.000 --> 16:22.000
Campion.

16:22.000 --> 16:23.000
I said step away!

16:23.000 --> 16:24.000
She's not

16:23.000 --> 16:24.000
going to hurt anyone.

16:24.000 --> 16:27.000
She is a weapon

16:24.000 --> 16:27.000
of mass destruction.

16:27.000 --> 16:28.000
She kidnapped

16:27.000 --> 16:28.000
these kids.

16:28.000 --> 16:30.000
No!

16:28.000 --> 16:30.000
She's a good Mother!

16:30.000 --> 16:32.000
-Vita, move!

16:30.000 --> 16:32.000
-Don't shoot!

