36:30.000 --> 36:32.000
Sol is a lie.

36:33.000 --> 36:36.000
But I suddenly

36:33.000 --> 36:36.000
understood how

36:36.000 --> 36:37.000
when people can't believe

36:36.000 --> 36:37.000
their luck,

36:38.000 --> 36:41.000
they have to make up a god

36:38.000 --> 36:41.000
to thank for it.

36:41.000 --> 36:49.000
♪♪

36:49.000 --> 36:56.000
♪♪

36:56.000 --> 37:00.000
[ Sighs ]

37:00.000 --> 37:04.000
There.

37:00.000 --> 37:04.000
That's enough.

37:04.000 --> 37:05.000
Are you feeling it?

37:05.000 --> 37:08.000
Yes.

37:08.000 --> 37:10.000
Thank you.

37:10.000 --> 37:17.000
♪♪

37:17.000 --> 37:23.000
♪♪

37:24.000 --> 37:26.000
[ Indistinct whispering ]

37:26.000 --> 37:35.000
♪♪

37:35.000 --> 37:44.000
♪♪

37:44.000 --> 37:53.000
♪♪

37:53.000 --> 38:02.000
♪♪

38:02.000 --> 38:11.000
♪♪

38:11.000 --> 38:20.000
♪♪

38:20.000 --> 38:29.000
♪♪

38:29.000 --> 38:38.000
♪♪

38:38.000 --> 38:40.000
Praise Sol.

38:40.000 --> 38:43.000
[ Indistinct whispering ]

38:43.000 --> 38:49.000
♪♪

38:55.000 --> 39:00.000
♪♪

39:00.000 --> 39:02.000
Want to hear a secret?

39:02.000 --> 39:04.000
♪♪

39:04.000 --> 39:07.000
Sure.

39:07.000 --> 39:12.000
♪♪

39:12.000 --> 39:14.000
Sol put that baby

39:12.000 --> 39:14.000
inside Mother.

39:14.000 --> 39:16.000
♪♪

39:16.000 --> 39:19.000
How do you know?

39:19.000 --> 39:21.000
I can just feel it.

39:21.000 --> 39:23.000
♪♪

39:23.000 --> 39:25.000
He's not evil,

39:23.000 --> 39:25.000
like you said.

39:25.000 --> 39:27.000
♪♪

39:27.000 --> 39:29.000
He's trying

39:27.000 --> 39:29.000
to help us.

39:29.000 --> 39:32.000
♪♪

39:32.000 --> 39:36.000
And this baby is gonna

39:32.000 --> 39:36.000
change everything.

39:36.000 --> 39:41.000
♪♪

39:41.000 --> 39:46.000
♪♪

39:46.000 --> 39:48.000
You know

39:46.000 --> 39:48.000
I killed him.

39:48.000 --> 39:50.000
Yes, Tempest.

39:50.000 --> 39:56.000
♪♪

39:56.000 --> 39:57.000
It moved.

39:57.000 --> 40:03.000
♪♪

40:03.000 --> 40:04.000
It's alive.

40:04.000 --> 40:07.000
♪♪

40:07.000 --> 40:08.000
Thank you.

40:08.000 --> 40:15.000
♪♪

40:15.000 --> 40:21.000
♪♪

40:21.000 --> 40:22.000
Lucius: Has Sol spoken to you

40:21.000 --> 40:22.000
yet, Your Eminence?

40:23.000 --> 40:26.000
Has He told you

40:23.000 --> 40:26.000
where we're headed?

40:26.000 --> 40:30.000
It seems He doesn't quite

40:26.000 --> 40:30.000
favor you as He once did.

40:30.000 --> 40:32.000
He tests us.

40:32.000 --> 40:36.000
Dorian was more than

40:32.000 --> 40:36.000
a test.

40:36.000 --> 40:38.000
We will pray

40:36.000 --> 40:38.000
for his soul.

40:38.000 --> 40:40.000
But you obviously

40:38.000 --> 40:40.000
deemed him impure.

40:40.000 --> 40:42.000
Yes.

40:42.000 --> 40:44.000
All the more reason

40:42.000 --> 40:44.000
to pray for him.

40:44.000 --> 40:49.000
♪♪

40:49.000 --> 40:52.000
You're upset.

40:52.000 --> 40:56.000
Perhaps you should stay quiet

40:52.000 --> 40:56.000
until you recovered your senses.

40:56.000 --> 40:58.000
♪♪

40:58.000 --> 41:02.000
Did you pray for my father

40:58.000 --> 41:02.000
after you executed him?

41:02.000 --> 41:05.000
Did you pray for his soul?

41:05.000 --> 41:07.000
Of course.

41:08.000 --> 41:11.000
Do you see any resemblance

41:08.000 --> 41:11.000
between us, my father and I?

41:11.000 --> 41:15.000
♪♪

41:15.000 --> 41:16.000
Just a simple question,

41:16.000 --> 41:18.000
one you should have

41:16.000 --> 41:18.000
no trouble answering.

41:18.000 --> 41:21.000
♪♪

41:21.000 --> 41:23.000
A true Mithraic would never

41:23.000 --> 41:25.000
pray for a soul

41:23.000 --> 41:25.000
he deemed impure.

41:25.000 --> 41:28.000
♪♪

41:28.000 --> 41:32.000
What the necromancer said

41:28.000 --> 41:32.000
is true, isn't it?

41:32.000 --> 41:35.000
You're not

41:32.000 --> 41:35.000
Marcus Drusus.

41:35.000 --> 41:36.000
So who the hell

41:35.000 --> 41:36.000
are you?

41:36.000 --> 41:40.000
♪♪

41:40.000 --> 41:42.000
You all wanted

41:40.000 --> 41:42.000
to be deceived.

41:42.000 --> 41:47.000
♪♪

41:47.000 --> 41:49.000
You're nothing

41:47.000 --> 41:49.000
but a bunch of sheep --

41:49.000 --> 41:54.000
all of you --

41:49.000 --> 41:54.000
unworthy of Sol's love.

41:54.000 --> 41:56.000
You see, all I did was lead you

41:54.000 --> 41:56.000
back to the light.

41:57.000 --> 41:59.000
♪♪

41:59.000 --> 42:01.000
It doesn't matter

41:59.000 --> 42:01.000
who I am.

42:01.000 --> 42:04.000
♪♪

42:04.000 --> 42:10.000
All that matters is that

42:04.000 --> 42:10.000
He chose me to be king.

42:10.000 --> 42:18.000
♪♪

42:18.000 --> 42:20.000
Then He will surely

42:18.000 --> 42:20.000
protect you, then.

42:21.000 --> 42:23.000
♪♪

42:23.000 --> 42:25.000
[ Growls ]

42:25.000 --> 42:31.000
♪♪

42:31.000 --> 42:37.000
♪♪

42:37.000 --> 42:39.000
Let Sol's will be done.

42:39.000 --> 42:49.000
♪♪

42:49.000 --> 42:58.000
♪♪

